snippet.title: Aaron The Little Detective | Nintendo Switch Gameplay
snippet.description:
Aaron The Little Detective can be enjoyed by kids of all ages. Thanks to the full voice interface, even babies can search for hidden pictures on their own. Therefore, even if you can't read the text, you can get a sense of accomplishment.
